This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and sentiment analysis of tweets. The use of deep learning models and attention mechanisms also suggests that it could belong to the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves transfer learning, which could place it in the sub-category of cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
